ly from filesystem (markdown files, git repos, JSON configs)\\n- **Tech stack:** React 19 + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS v4 + Express.js (matching SocialHomes patterns)\\n\\n## Data Sources (per project directory)\\n| Source | Data Extracted |\\n|--------|---------------|\\n| `git log/status/branch` | Branch, commits, dirty files, remote URL |\\n| `CLAUDE.md` | Project description, tech stack, commands |\\n| `SESSION-HISTORY.md` | Agent sessions, what was done, pending work |\\n| `DEV-FIX-LIST.md` | Test pass rate, bugs (P1-P4), warnings |\\n| `EXECUTION-PLAN.md` | Phase progress, task counts, completion % |\\n| `DEVOPS.md` | Cloud Run config, deployment URL, costs |\\n| `.claude/settings.json` | Hooks (Entire.io etc.) |\\n| `.mcp.json` | MCP servers (Telegram etc.) |\\n| `package.json` | Project name, scripts, dependencies |\\n| `cloudbuild.yaml` / `Dockerfile` | CI/CD presence |\\n\\n## UI Design\\n\\n### View 1: All Projects Grid (`/`)\\n- **Stats row:** Total projects, Active (7d), Open bugs, Bootstrapped count\\n- **Project cards** in a responsive grid, each showing:\\n  - Name + status indicator (green=active, amber=stale, grey=unconfigured)\\n  - Git branch + last commit time + message\\n  - Test pass rate + bug count + warning count\\n  - Current phase with mini progress bar\\n  - Click to drill into detail\\n\\n### View 2: Project Detail (`/projects/:name`)\\nTabbed layout with 5 sections:\\n\\n| Tab | Content |\\n|-----|---------|\\n| **Overview** | Git branch, last 20 commits, description, tech stack badges, build commands |\\n| **Progress** | Execution plan phases as progress bars, task breakdown, overall % |\\n| **Quality** | Test pass rate gauge, bug list with severity badges, warning list |\\n| **Sessions** | Timeline of agent sessions (expandable), pending work items |\\n| **Infrastructure** | MCP servers, hooks, deployment config, CI/CD status |\\n\\n### Bootstrap Panel\\n- Un-configured projects show an \\\"Initialize Project\\\" button\\n- Creates template files: CLAUDE.md, SESSION-HISTORY.md, DEV-FIX-LIST.md, EXECUTION-PLAN.md, .claude/settings.json\\n\\n## File Structure\\n```\\nmission-control/\\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 app/\\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 src/\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 pages/\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 ProjectsPage.tsx        # Main grid view\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 ProjectDetailPage.tsx   # Tabbed detail view\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 components/\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 layout/Layout.tsx       # Header + outlet (no sidebar)\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 ProjectCard.tsx         # Grid card per project\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 StatsRow.tsx            # Summary stats\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 BootstrapModal.tsx      # Initialize project dialog\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 detail/\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502       \u251c\u2500\u2500 OverviewTab.tsx     # Git + description\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502       \u251c\u2500\u2500 ProgressTab.tsx     # Phase progress bars\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502       \u251c\u2500\u2500 QualityTab.tsx      # Tests + bugs\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502       \u251c\u2500\u2500 SessionsTab.tsx     # Agent activity timeline\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2502       \u2514\u2500\u2500 InfraTab.tsx        # MCP, hooks, deployment\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 services/api.ts            # Fetch wrapper\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 types/index.ts             # Shared interfaces\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 App.tsx                     # Router (2 routes)\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 main.tsx                    # Entry + React Query\\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 index.css                  # Tailwind v4 theme (copied from SocialHomes)\\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 index.html\\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 vite.config.ts\\n\u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 package.json\\n\u25