ypes + scanner + git-reader | `server/src/types/`, `scanner.ts`, `git-reader.ts` |\\n| 3 | Markdown parser (highest complexity) | `markdown-parser.ts` |\\n| 4 | Config reader | `config-reader.ts` |\\n| 5 | Express server + API routes | `index.ts`, `routes/projects.ts` |\\n| 6 | Frontend theme + layout + router | `index.css`, `Layout.tsx`, `App.tsx`, `main.tsx` |\\n| 7 | Projects grid page + cards | `ProjectsPage.tsx`, `ProjectCard.tsx`, `StatsRow.tsx` |\\n| 8 | Project detail page + all 5 tabs | `ProjectDetailPage.tsx`, `detail/*.tsx` |\\n| 9 | Bootstrap service + modal | `bootstrap.ts`, `BootstrapModal.tsx` |\\n| 10 | Polish \u2014 auto-refresh, error states, loading skeletons | Various |\\n\\n## Styling\\n- Dark theme matching SocialHomes (copy `index.css` theme tokens)\\n- Brand teal accent, peach headings, Inter + Space Grotesk fonts\\n- Glass-card effect on project cards\\n- Status colours: green (passing), amber (warning), red (critical)\\n\\n## Verification\\n1. `cd /mnt/c/.netapps/mission-control/server && npm run dev` \u2014 server starts on 3001\\n2. `cd /mnt/c/.netapps/mission-control/app && npm run dev` \u2014 Vite starts on 5174\\n3. Open `http://localhost:5174` \u2014 projects grid loads with SocialHomes + other directories\\n4. Click SocialHomes card \u2014 detail view shows git commits, test results, phase progress, sessions\\n5. Click an unconfigured project \u2014 bootstrap button appears and creates template files\\n6. `GET http://localhost:3001/api/projects` returns JSON with all project summaries\\n\\n\\nIf you need specific details from before exiting plan mode (like exact code snippets, error messages, or content you generated), read the full transcript at: /home/rajiv/.REDACTED.jsonl\"},\"uuid\":\"146cc0c3-282d-4286-a5cf-f075e6f2e0ea\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-14T14:55:08.378Z\",\"planContent\":\"# Mission Control - Developer Command Centre\\n\\n## Context\\nYou manage multiple projects under `/mnt/c/.netapps/` and need a single dashboard to v